    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic iacet Amanti<lb break="no" n="2"/>a qui <note>sic</note> vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> III <expan><abbr>men</abbr><ex>ses</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>VIII <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>iem</ex></expan> I titulum po<lb break="no" n="4"/>suit Vetranio et <lb n="5"/>Lea in pace
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwischen dem Namen Lea in Z. 5 und der folgenden Phrase in pace Darstellung eines Christograms.</p>
            </div>
